<item>
            <title>[OAK-2289] Async indexer checkpoints not cleaned up under heavy load</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2289</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Under heavy load &lt;tt&gt;NodeStore#release&lt;/tt&gt; might return &lt;tt&gt;false&lt;/tt&gt;. In these cases the asynx indexer leaks the affected checkpoint.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
