                            <comment id="14223155" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Mon, 24 Nov 2014 17:19:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;good catch! I think the issue is here &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;, we might only need to add the checkpoint to the list, as the comment already implies.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (cp.equals(checkpoint)) {
  temps.add(cp);
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;continue&lt;/span&gt;;
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-oak/blob/trunk/oak-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/oak/plugins/index/AsyncIndexUpdate.java#L205&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-oak/blob/trunk/oak-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/oak/plugins/index/AsyncIndexUpdate.java#L205&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14223613" author="mduerig" created="Mon, 24 Nov 2014 22:07:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Proposed patch. The patch ensures the &lt;tt&gt;beforeCheckpoint&lt;/tt&gt; will be deleted even when the &lt;tt&gt;NodeStore#release&lt;/tt&gt; fails. With the patch I didn&apos;t observe the issue any more.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14224243" author="mduerig" created="Tue, 25 Nov 2014 08:49:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in trunk at &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1641541&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1641541&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Fixed in 1.0 branch at &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1641542&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1641542&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
